title: Junkies In Baton Rouge W DCYoungFly Chico Bean & Karlous Miller | Ep. 214

description:
Junkies challenge DC to a dance battle in Louisiana and the whole squad goes in! Only at the 85 South Show will you see the three funniest young comedians in the game combine to bring the laughs! DC Young Fly, Karlous Miller, and Chico Bean perform a show entirely comprised of improv roasting, freestyling and off the dome comedy!
